---
name: neo4j-best-practices.mdc
description: Best practices for Neo4j database management and query optimization
globs: **/*.cypher
---

- Use uniqueness constraints to ensure data integrity and improve query performance.
- Create appropriate indexes on frequently queried properties to speed up lookups.
- Utilize the `MERGE` command to avoid duplicate nodes and relationships.
- Optimize Cypher queries by using pattern matching and avoiding Cartesian products.
- Regularly monitor and analyze query performance using the Neo4j query log.
